34601.name: Honoured Tattoo of the Berserker
stats: You gain Onslaught for 4 seconds on Hit
reminderText: (Onslaught grants 20% increased Attack, Cast, and Movement Speed)

items.name: One With Nothing
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Small, Medium or Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Once you begin to rely on your weapons,
You ensure you can't live without them.

118.name: Hollow Palm Technique
stats:
You count as Dual Wielding while you are Unencumbered
40% more Attack Speed with Melee Skills while you are Unencumbered
Adds 14 to 20 Attack Physical Damage to Melee Skills per 10 Dexterity while you are Unencumbered
reminderText: (You are Unencumbered while you have no Gloves, no Main Hand Item, and no Off Hand Item Equipped)
flavourText: "The mastodons of yore were each born with two weapons greater than any sword. So, too, were you." - Maraketh Proverb
